    Have you ever Ray-Traced, or maybe you want to ?
    
    NO ? Then stop reading and delete it all !

    YES ? Oh, the fun begins...
    Here we go... You sit down and starts to make your object. 
    The modeling couldn't be better. You sit there for hours and when 
    you think that you are ready you cant find ANY good textures. 
    Well, here is the solution to your problem. EXTREME Textures. 
    A superb serie with all 24BIT-JPG textures. The series will
    have following titles:
    
    Construction -> Materials
    Fabrics      -> Papers
    Humans       -> Animals
    Metals
    Patterns     -> Fractals
    Plastic      -> Rubbers
    Stone
    Woods        -> Plants
    Earth        -> Sky         -> Weathers
    Liquids
